        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer126743" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13342675848092139792">Not my favorite. It’s very plot-heavy, and I’m a character-development lover. I love the descriptions of Berlin and I wish I’d had a map to trace where he was at every move. That said, he knew far too much of Berlin far too well. The city is much bigger than Kanon makes it out to be. I do like the way in which he tackles guilt, remorse, and Vergangenheitsbewaltigung.</span>

